<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Xavfsizlik on RailTech</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/xavfsizlik/</link><description>Recent content in Xavfsizlik on RailTech</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>uz</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/xavfsizlik/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>O'zbekiston temir yo'llari uchun harakat xavfsizligi tizimlari</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/uty-safety-systems/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/uty-safety-systems/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Loyiha haqida
 &lt;div id="loyiha-haqida" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#loyiha-haqida" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2023-yilda «RailTech» AJ «O&amp;rsquo;zbekiston temir yo&amp;rsquo;llari» buyurtmasiga binoan zamonaviy harakat xavfsizligi tizimlarini yetkazib berish va joriy etish bo&amp;rsquo;yicha yirik loyihani amalga oshirdi.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Vazifa
 &lt;div id="vazifa" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#vazifa" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O&amp;rsquo;zbekiston temir yo&amp;rsquo;l tarmoqining ayrim uchastkalarida mavjud xavfsizlik tizimlarini zamonaviy uskunalarga almashtirish va poyezd harakatining xavfsizligini oshirish.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Amalga oshirilgan ishlar
 &lt;div id="amalga-oshirilgan-ishlar" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#amalga-oshirilgan-ishlar" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mavjud tizimlarni tahlil qilish va texnik topshiriqni ishlab chiqish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Zamonaviy signalizatsiya va xavfsizlik uskunalarini tanlash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uskunalarni xorijdan yetkazib berish va bojxona rasmiylashtiruvi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;O&amp;rsquo;rnatish va sozlash ishlarida texnik nazorat&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Xodimlarni yangi uskunalar bilan ishlashga o&amp;rsquo;qitish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Natijalar
 &lt;div id="natijalar" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#natijalar" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Loyiha muvaffaqiyatli yakunlandi. Yangi tizimlar poyezd harakatining xavfsizligini sezilarli darajada oshirdi va xalqaro standartlarga muvofiqlikni ta&amp;rsquo;minladi.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/uty-safety-systems/featured.jpg"/></item><item><title>O'zbekistonda temir yo'l xavfsizligi: zamonaviy yondashuvlar</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/blog/railway-safety-uzbekistan/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/blog/railway-safety-uzbekistan/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;O&amp;rsquo;zbekistonda temir yo&amp;rsquo;l xavfsizligi
 &lt;div id="ozbekistonda-temir-yol-xavfsizligi" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#ozbekistonda-temir-yol-xavfsizligi" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Temir yo&amp;rsquo;l transporti O&amp;rsquo;zbekiston iqtisodiyotida muhim o&amp;rsquo;rin tutadi. Yuk va yo&amp;rsquo;lovchi tashish hajmlarining o&amp;rsquo;sishi bilan harakat xavfsizligi masalalari tobora dolzarb bo&amp;rsquo;lib bormoqda.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Mavjud holat
 &lt;div id="mavjud-holat" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#mavjud-holat" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O&amp;rsquo;zbekiston temir yo&amp;rsquo;l tarmog&amp;rsquo;i so&amp;rsquo;nggi yillarda sezilarli modernizatsiya jarayonidan o&amp;rsquo;tmoqda. Yangi yuqori tezlikli yo&amp;rsquo;nalishlar ochildi, tarkib yangilandi va infratuzilma takomillashtirildi. Biroq xavfsizlik tizimlari sohasida hali amalga oshirilishi kerak bo&amp;rsquo;lgan ishlar ko&amp;rsquo;p.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Zamonaviy xavfsizlik texnologiyalari
 &lt;div id="zamonaviy-xavfsizlik-texnologiyalari" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#zamonaviy-xavfsizlik-texnologiyalari" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bugungi kunda dunyo temir yo&amp;rsquo;l sanoatida quyidagi xavfsizlik texnologiyalari keng qo&amp;rsquo;llanilmoqda:&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/blog/railway-safety-uzbekistan/featured.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>